
== SOURCE
https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-54538228

== AGENT
IBM Research & Pfizer

== GOAL
Predict early Alzheimer signs from Cookie Drawing Test

== DATA
The samples used by IBM came from The Framingham Heart Study, a US research project into 5,000 people and their families that has been ongoing since 1948.

== METHODS
Supervised

== RESULTS
Slightly positive results. Better than not knowing but not hugely successful

== ISSUES
All research carried out by IBM and Pfizer employees, thus could be biased in order to secure funding

== SCORE
4. Not very cool as not very conclusive. 

== COMMENTS
Not very conclusive, in their own words their study shows "subtle early sings of progression" of Alzheimer, so not very conclusive